IZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人有興趣又或者有介紹<br />\n我會去悉尼同黃金海岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n Wollongong skydive 試過<br />\n個陣係官網買<br />\n有時有early bird discount<br />\n同埋有唔同package<br />\n要睇啱<br />\n仲有skydive 好睇天氣<br />\n最後預兩日just in case</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無知一問<br />\n唔好天會唔會俾第二日你重跳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會 跳傘要安排起行程最早</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當日我改咗3 次fyi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過冇話要錢改期<br />\n同埋sydney 去 wollongong 要預兩個鐘<br />\n除非你 係wollongong 訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇見佢有shuttle 應該ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係個度跳過，個景麻麻，同埋如果你走既時候都坐佢shuttle返悉尼要等到下就3,4點"}]}